These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, water
There are 7 different favourite colors: azure, emerald, ivory, ebony, apricot, blood-red, amber
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, chef, mechanic, scientist, designer, photographer, manager
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, colombian, malaysian, spanish, italian, german
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the fisherman##1
 3. the canadian is the designer##1
 4. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
 5. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
 6. the colombian is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the dutch is on the right of the spanish##1
 9. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the spanish##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
13. the person who likes apricot is in the middle##1
14. the photographer is on the left of the mechanic##1
15. the german is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
16. the designer is on the left of the photographer##1
17. the italian is on the right of the german##1
18. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the scientist##1
19. the colombian is in the middle##1
20. the scientist is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
21. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Beverage      | fanta    | 7up     | water  | lemonade   | iced-tea | juice      | cola          |
| Color   | amber    | ebony   | blood-red  | apricot       | azure  | emerald      | ivory     |
| Job         | fisherman | chef | designer | photographer | mechanic   | scientist     | manager |
| Nationality     | german      | italian   | canadian   | colombian  | malaysian  | spanish | dutch       |

